  "riddle": "1. Unearth the date when a devoted health and wellness champion began her service in provincial leadership — who is she?\n\n2. What assembly, comprised of representatives shaping policy in this province, boasts a significant count of its members?\n\n3. Seek the earth beneath the provincial assembly — how high does it rise above sea level?\n\n4. Discover how many museums share their knowledge nearby this provincial seat of power.\n\n5. Take the elevation you found in clue 3 and combine it with the number of those cultural institutions you uncovered in clue 4 — what new value emerges?\n\n6. A gathering place for nature and relaxation flourishes near the assembly. How many parks can you find in that vicinity?\n\n7. The previous result from clue 6, now turned into a Roman numeral, reveals a new perspective—how many characters comprise that numeral?\n\n8. Transitioning from Celsius to Fahrenheit, how warm is the temperature set at 73 degrees in the Fahrenheit scale?\n\n9. Venture to the title of the national seat of governance and unveil how high it stands in the world — what elevation does it register?\n\n10. With your newfound height from clue 9, investigate how many 1-bits are revealed in its binary representation.\n\n11. Count the days from the start of October in 2022 until mid-March in 2026 — how many days does this span?\n\n12. Now, compute the absolute difference between the height you found in clue 3 and that in clue 9, then reduce it by taking the modulo 10 of this difference. What single digit emerges from the calculation based on clues 3 and 9?",
